metadata.name: Teenage Mutant Paper Turtles
metadata.description:
"Teenage Mutant Paper Turtles" was a concept that I saw on the internet and as an origami,
and I thought of bringing it to the 3D world.
I had the pleasure of collaborating with Emad Ameri for making the video.
the model is made in 3Ds Max, baked in Marmoset, and textured in Substance Painter.
The video was made and edited with Cinema4D, OctanceRender, and After Effects.
